body.name: ZER-LON GeForce GTX 1660 Super 6GB Graphics Cards, GDRR6 192Bit PCIE 3.0X16 Computer Gaming Gpu, Dual Freeze Fans Video Card with HDMI/DP/DVI Ports Support 4K and 8K HD
deliveryMessages: Or fastest delivery Wednesday, February 14. Order within 14 hrs 46 mins
features: 【Amazing Gaminig Experience】GTX 1660 Super graphics card is a mainstream gaming GPU built on the 12 nm process, equipped with 192-Bit and 6GB GDDR6 memory with 1750 MHz. Providing computer enthusiasts with a smoother, higher quality gaming experience.

【High Definition Display Effect 】GTX 1660S 6GB Graphics Card has 3 monitor support ouput included 1X DVI Port+ 1X Display Port + 1X HDMI Port, can support three monitors. GTX 1660 super is connected to the rest of the system using a PCI-Express 3.0 x16 interface, supports up to 8K display, delivers more higher definition pc gaming effect.

【Powerful Cooling Performance】ZER LON cooling system uses a combination of traditional grooved and copper powder sintered composite heat pipes that directly contact the GPU core to quickly export core heat. At the same time, the integrated thermal design makes the core, memory, power supply MOS tube and the heatsink fully in contact, effectively reducing the working temperature, avoiding MOS tube overheating caused by full load degradation and other reasons, thus improving the stability and life

【3D Intelligent Fan Control System】The fan will remain off during light core loads or when the core temperature is low. This is a game of temperature and noise It brings gamers a cool and low-noise experience!
【What You Will Get】1x GTX 1660 Super 6GB graphics card, 2-Year Limited warranty, professional after-sale service.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Brand Story ZER-LON was founded by a group of computer enthusiasts who were frustrated with the lack of quality graphics cards available in the market. They believed that gamers and other computer users deserved more powerful and efficient graphics technology, so they decided to create their own brand. ZER-LON is known as one of the graphics card brands in the industry. The team remains true to their original vision of providing high-quality graphics technology to gamers and computer enthusiasts around the world. With each new release, they strive to push the boundaries of what is possible, offering unparalleled performance and capabilities that set ZER-LON apart from its competitors.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great card for the price.
reviews.reviewText: Excellent budget card. Works as well as much pricier cards I've had installed. Easy install and the FPS has yet to slow down on some of my most demanding cards. Don't let the no frills look fool you. Great card.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great value, card was as promised.
reviews.reviewText: The graphics card arrived on time and without any signs of damage. It was easily installed and has worked great since. I'd be happy to purchase a ZER-LON card again if needed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Overall a great card for a cheap price.
reviews.reviewText: For this price, it is basically a steal, I bought this originally for my little brothers rig(a budget build), and thought none of since it was such a low price, but to my surprise the stress test did really well and passed my expectations. As for time being I'm sure it should last time a good amount of time before he could actually upgrade to a better card. Overall 10/10 would highly recommend for a budget build that is looking to be upgraded in the future.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Graphics Card
reviews.reviewText: Bought this for my old HP Omen which had a 1060 which was fine for most games on low, but with the newer games struggled even on low settings, I looked into upgrading and found the 1660 Super to be a good fit without having to change out other components of my computer. Install was super easy and almost plug and play, since then many of my games like have been running smooth and even newer games have almost no issue with low to mid settings. Been using it for a few months with no issues, I am very happy with this purchase and a good budget card for what I want.
